<div class="form-group col-sm-12 no-padding">
    <label>Program Cost (Mandatory, Non-refundable) <span class="required">*</span><br /><small>The program cost includes funds to cover arrangements for delegates during the medical mission including medications</small></label>
    <div class="input-group col-sm-12">
        <input type="checkbox" name="program_cost" value="Non-refundable $150 (Mandatory for all applicants)" /> Non-refundable $150 (Mandatory for all applicants)
        <div class="error program_cost"></div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="form-group col-sm-12 no-padding">
    <label>Additional Donation (Tax-deductible to the fullest extent of US law) <span class="required">*</span></label>
    <div class="input-group col-sm-12">
        <input type="radio" name="additional_donation" value="To help offset the costs of medications, supplies and arrangements for this mission, I will donate $250" /> To help offset the costs of medications, supplies and arrangements for this mission, I will donate $250
    </div>
    <div class="input-group col-sm-12">
        <input type="radio" name="additional_donation" value="To help offset the costs of medications, supplies and arrangements for this mission, I will donate $500" /> To help offset the costs of medications, supplies and arrangements for this mission, I will donate $500
    </div>
    <div class="input-group col-sm-12">
        <input type="radio" name="additional_donation" value="I will donate a different amount via www.imamiamedics.com/donate now or donate at a later time" /> I will donate a different amount via www.imamiamedics.com/donate now or donate at a later time
    </div>
    <div class="input-group col-sm-12">
        <div class="error additional_donation"></div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="form-group col-sm-12 no-padding">
    <label>Accommodations Option (You must select one) <span class="required">*</span><br><small>To view details on the CaravaneSajadiya IMI kafla, please click here: http://bit.ly/imiarbaeen9</small></label>
    <div class="input-group col-sm-12">
        <input type="radio" name="accomodation_option" value="I will be traveling and staying with the group." /> I will be traveling and staying with the group.
    </div>
    <div class="input-group col-sm-12">
